summary: This document is a declaration of the custodian of records in response to a Grand Jury Subpoena issued by Assistant United States Attorney Maurene Conley. It certifies the authenticity of records provided in compliance with the subpoena, affirming that they were created in the regular course of business and are accurate.

persons.name: Maurene Conley
persons.context: Maurene Conley issued a Grand Jury Subpoena requesting specific records.

persons.name: one Bey
persons.context: The individual who signed the declaration certifying the records in response to the subpoena.

events.title: Grand Jury Subpoena Issued
events.description: A Grand Jury Subpoena was issued by Assistant United States Attorney Maurene Conley requesting specified records.

keyFacts: The document is a declaration made under penalty of perjury.
It certifies that the records provided were made at or near the time of the events they describe.
The declaration affirms that the records were kept in the course of regularly conducted business activity.
